Package: checkr
Type: Package
Title: Facilities for checking R submissions in tutorials
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Daniel Kaplan
Maintainer: Daniel Kaplan <kaplan@macalester.edu>
Description: Packages such as tutor support interactive documents that serve as tutorials in which students can submit R code and get feedback on correctness. This package provides facilities for specifying what tests should be run on the submitted code, and also provides an interface to the tutor system.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), magrittr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: learnr, testthat, dplyr,
    knitr, stringr, compare, sourcetools,
    rmarkdown, ggplot2, lazyeval
Imports: jsonlite, googlesheets
VignetteBuilder: knitr
